{"tid":236143,"cid":35,"subCid":0,"title":"村屋仔上網慘過乞米","createTime":"2017-05-09T13:34:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-12T19:05:37.000Z","uid":7651,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cd27f0c54c37b881489c65016fa0e8989a67219c","tid":236143,"uid":7651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T13:34:24.000Z","msg":"話說一直用緊網x行嘅電話線上網,合約就嚟到期<br />\n速度慢不在話下(住得村屋預左),但一行雷閃電落雨就好大機會燒modem或者斷網線<br />\n一年起碼要約5,6次師傅上嚟整<br />\n整到個師傅都認得路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就算平日好天,條網線都唔知痴左咩總掣,斷下斷下咁<br />\n有時打個機都會突然斷線爆ping,同fd打機都覺得唔好意思,因為我又停左係到郁唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想係條村搵夠20戶人再同寬頻公司傾拉光纖,啲廢老又唔肯,叫我去m記借wifi<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n暗串左佢幾句仲發爛渣,班後生嘅又唔上水覆機<br />\ngoogle完見到有兩隻router可以插sim卡放wifi,一隻asus一隻tp-link<br />\n想問下有冇手足用緊?<br />\n另外有冇sales有啲上網plan可以介紹下<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18b98819cd6c8a7c79bda31bcab2cbe025c80a0b","tid":236143,"uid":92001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T13:35:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"124fb26fa7ac647670da6df5c849bdbe7cbbfc4e","tid":236143,"uid":9093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T13:43:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"205aeb66ed83e05ac52685d55f4ea11fb00ab1e3","tid":236143,"uid":9093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T13:43:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"62a270ceb5d9c3e9750bdf6ad6aa97405678f275","tid":236143,"uid":28796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T13:48:03.000Z","msg":"用CSL 無限plan上網啦。<br />\n收得幾差都唔只6mb。upload又快幾百倍。<br />\nRouter我用華為。"},{"pid":"c82020918eb433150a6d8bc49dce26c86c9080fa","tid":236143,"uid":100014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T13:49:33.000Z","msg":"Don't do it. The mobile sim card disconnects quite often... cannot play online games."},{"pid":"7b965319028a0ca0d9730a4b5639d9ec4de87d76","tid":236143,"uid":7651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T13:54:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用CSL 無限plan上網啦。<br />\n收得幾差都唔只6mb。upload又快幾百倍。<br />\nRouter我用華為。</blockquote><br />\n巴打個無限plan同router咩價位到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?"},{"pid":"3e84ca951433c09742ab42ef4ace87526f2f6969","tid":236143,"uid":7651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T13:55:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Don't do it. The mobile sim card disconnects quite often... cannot play online games.</blockquote><br />\n巴打用過?我都算住得入,怕收得差<br />\n但而家用電話線上網真係差到無得再差,斷線多過食飯"},{"pid":"dfd27f28dbf0bb4b2722a01e637041e5fc536603","tid":236143,"uid":28796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T14:02:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>用CSL 無限plan上網啦。<br />\n收得幾差都唔只6mb。upload又快幾百倍。<br />\nRouter我用華為。</blockquote><br />\n巴打個無限plan同router咩價位到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我嗰陣上台$460左右。全速無限plan，唔知而家咩價。<br />\nRouter 就$2000左右。要搵隻行到用sim card 300mb以上。<br />\n斷線都真係會，但用網上行都打唔到機㗎啦。<br />\n轉咗真係打得好q順。順既機會係提升90%<br />\n你自己搵個fd用csl既，去你屋企test下網速先啦。<br />\n其實我屋企收得最快都係百幾mb。<br />\n但我已經好滿足。睇youtube高清唔駛等既感覺真係網上行俾唔到。"},{"pid":"2f714e2b82b1ee1871edd711f2f4d7443b517748","tid":236143,"uid":7651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T14:11:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>用CSL 無限plan上網啦。<br />\n收得幾差都唔只6mb。upload又快幾百倍。<br />\nRouter我用華為。</blockquote><br />\n巴打個無限plan同router咩價位到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我嗰陣上台$460左右。全速無限plan，唔知而家咩價。<br />\nRouter 就$2000左右。要搵隻行到用sim card 300mb以上。<br />\n斷線都真係會，但用網上行都打唔到機㗎啦。<br />\n轉咗真係打得好q順。順既機會係提升90%<br />\n你自己搵個fd用csl既，去你屋企test下網速先啦。<br />\n其實我屋企收得最快都係百幾mb。<br />\n但我已經好滿足。睇youtube高清唔駛等既感覺真係網上行俾唔到。</blockquote><br />\n好羨慕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔該晒巴打，好詳盡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e559909742756855e72bdc7c3a80b63c2630efd","tid":236143,"uid":111590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T14:13:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6ec5a7b36f12d9d3c8a9e699d43753c1771981c9","tid":236143,"uid":9093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T14:14:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5ca3347a05dc5e71a6cd4a03201c43a039cf9f90","tid":236143,"uid":59398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T14:20:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>話說一直用緊網x行嘅電話線上網,合約就嚟到期<br />\n速度慢不在話下(住得村屋預左),但一行雷閃電落雨就好大機會燒modem或者斷網線<br />\n一年起碼要約5,6次師傅上嚟整<br />\n整到個師傅都認得路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就算平日好天,條網線都唔知痴左咩總掣,斷下斷下咁<br />\n有時打個機都會突然斷線爆ping,同fd打機都覺得唔好意思,因為我又停左係到郁唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想係條村搵夠20戶人再同寬頻公司傾拉光纖,啲廢老又唔肯,叫我去m記借wifi<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n暗串左佢幾句仲發爛渣,班後生嘅又唔上水覆機<br />\ngoogle完見到有兩隻router可以插sim卡放wifi,一隻asus一隻tp-link<br />\n想問下有冇手足用緊?<br />\n另外有冇sales有啲上網plan可以介紹下<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n仲有隻叫華為<a href=\"http://m.intl.taobao.com/detail/detail.html?id=523029846957\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.intl.taobao.com%2Fdetail%2Fdetail.html%3Fid%3D523029846957&d=7oH93WZedTbABA3XB48d7ZWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=bd1945d6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://m.intl.taobao.com/detail/detail.html?id=523029846957</a><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/09/222047_f44ad3ea0287770026afd92937459d17.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F